{
  "stem": "10283.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said besides, we're going to go crazy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We can't just the two of us sit here for years and, and be hiding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we came out of hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And she looked for others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she had made some other friends,  a Belgian friend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was able to connect us with the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with an Underground [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] organization that really smuggled British prisoners of wars out of Germany through Switzerland and through Portugal and back to England.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow, she made a connection there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said, OK, you're the first woman that we do this for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because there were, like here, the coyotes, you know, like people that took people illegally to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it was very expensive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, they took thousands of dollars, or franks, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we didn't have that much money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She-- they gave us false papers like were born in-- we would have been born in Alsace-Lorraine, you know, in, Alsace-- what is it in English?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The border place between France and Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- these people didn't speak French so perfectly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had, like, a German accent like we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it would have been more plausible if we would have been caught that we didn't-- we spoke French by then, but not perfectly and certainly not without an accent.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had these false papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were preparing to leave, like, on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Wednesday before, we got a postcard from my father from Drancy that he's being deported.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the meantime, Petain had come to power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the south of France was no, no longer free.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was under Petain.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
